title: Looking Forward to the Not Warhammer 40,000 Preview Online
description: There's a Warhammer Preview Online coming, and there will be something for everyone! https://bit.ly/3NiLQaM

title: How to Paint: Battle Ready Black Templars Terminators
description:
Valiant warrior-knights, the Black Templars storm across the galaxy annihilating everything in their path. 

In this video we'll show you how to paint your Terminator in the colours of the Black Templars to a Battle Ready standard. We'll also show you some additional steps to take your miniature to the next level.  

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it


Don't forget to like, share and subscribe and to ring the bell to make sure you keep up to date with all our latest videos!

title: How to Paint Battle Ready Ultramarines Infernus Marine
description:
How to Paint: Battle Ready Ultramarines Infernus Marine Infernus Marines ensure no foe can escape the fiery wrath of their pyreblasters, and this step-by-step guide will help you paint yours in the colours of the Ultramarines using the Warhammer 40,000 Paints + Tools Set. 

We'll also add in some optional extras to make this paint job really stand out! If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it.

https://bit.ly/3JuSj1r
